24:23.795 --> 24:26.255
I heard you on the phone.

24:26.381 --> 24:30.050
We all have problems.

24:30.177 --> 24:33.387
You help-you help me with mine,
I help you with yours.

24:46.359 --> 24:47.693
No, keep it.

24:47.819 --> 24:49.737
Please, please.
Please, sir.

24:49.863 --> 24:52.865
Sir, in my-in my profession,
I see death every day,

24:52.991 --> 24:54.825
some by accident,
some by sickness,

24:54.951 --> 24:57.703
but some through despair.

24:57.829 --> 25:00.206
These are the ones
I wish I could have helped.

25:00.332 --> 25:02.041
Help me.

25:02.167 --> 25:05.127
Help me by pulling this trigger.

25:05.253 --> 25:06.670
Please.

25:06.796 --> 25:08.255
Come on, please.

25:08.381 --> 25:10.424
Please, I need your help.

25:10.550 --> 25:11.884
No.
- Please.

25:12.010 --> 25:13.886
Go ahead.
- I won't do it.

25:14.012 --> 25:16.722
I won't kill you.
No.

25:16.848 --> 25:19.225
Why?

25:19.351 --> 25:21.393
It's easy!

25:34.241 --> 25:38.827
I and my father are one?

25:38.954 --> 25:41.247
But can you feel my pain?

25:41.373 --> 25:45.209
Can you feel my pain?

25:47.796 --> 25:49.463
Hi. Hey.

25:49.589 --> 25:50.881
Hey.

25:51.007 --> 25:53.259
How's it feel to be my husband?

25:53.385 --> 25:56.387
Today, I must say that I'm
the happiest man in the world.

26:04.938 --> 26:07.523
Let me show you.

26:07.649 --> 26:11.151
Let me show the kids.

26:11.278 --> 26:14.738
Hey.

26:14.864 --> 26:16.490
I love you.

26:16.616 --> 26:18.576
I love you too.

26:27.627 --> 26:30.087
Charlie?

26:30.213 --> 26:33.591
Sorry to wake you, but we're-
we're closing down soon.

26:41.099 --> 26:42.057
Here.

26:42.183 --> 26:44.268
It's on the house.

26:44.394 --> 26:46.562
Just hope it might
cheer you up.

26:46.688 --> 26:48.147
You have a few minutes, so...

26:48.273 --> 26:51.150
or I could pack it up
to go for you.

26:51.276 --> 26:52.234
You want to share it?

26:52.360 --> 26:54.153
Share it with me?

26:54.279 --> 26:57.531
Oh.

26:57.657 --> 27:03.329
It's tempting, but I have this
new dress for the holiday

27:03.455 --> 27:05.372
that I'm determined to fit in.

27:05.498 --> 27:08.500
Want to know my secret?

27:08.627 --> 27:11.754
I hang it over the dining table
to help motivate me a bit.

27:16.635 --> 27:17.760
It's good, huh?

27:17.886 --> 27:18.844
Isn't it?

27:18.970 --> 27:21.930
We bake 'em fresh here
every morning.

27:22.057 --> 27:23.974
I think they're good.

27:27.771 --> 27:29.229
I don't mean to be nosy
or anything,

27:29.356 --> 27:33.400
but what's a man like you
doing at this hour

27:33.526 --> 27:37.529
passed out in a diner?

27:37.656 --> 27:40.616
I had a really hard day.

27:40.742 --> 27:44.244
Big smile like yours,
you expect me to believe that?

27:54.005 --> 27:55.839
Yeah, just right here.

27:55.965 --> 27:58.300
Okay.

27:58.426 --> 28:00.511
