28:12.607 --> 28:13.691
I like the lights.

28:13.817 --> 28:15.526
I did it myself.

28:15.652 --> 28:17.695
Yeah?

28:19.489 --> 28:21.115
I like the different colors.

28:21.241 --> 28:23.033
Yeah.

28:23.159 --> 28:25.327
Yeah, I've always
loved Christmas.

28:30.041 --> 28:31.792
You live there a long time?

28:31.918 --> 28:34.795
About a year,
since my divorce.

28:36.715 --> 28:38.006
You don't really
have to talk about that

28:38.133 --> 28:39.091
if you don't feel like it.

28:39.217 --> 28:40.217
I don't-

28:40.343 --> 28:43.262
Well, we-
you know, we grew apart.

28:43.388 --> 28:45.597
You know, you wake up
one morning after 13 years,

28:45.724 --> 28:47.474
and the feeling's gone,

28:47.600 --> 28:49.017
and, you know,
you try to hang in there,

28:49.144 --> 28:52.271
but there's really nothing
you can do.

28:52.397 --> 28:54.356
But we both agreed that,
you know,

28:54.482 --> 28:58.777
we didn't want to grow old
taking up each other's space.

28:58.903 --> 29:01.155
You guys still talk, then?

29:01.281 --> 29:02.823
Not for a couple months.

29:07.495 --> 29:08.954
Do you-

29:09.080 --> 29:11.373
do you want to come up,
'cause I'm just-

29:11.499 --> 29:14.460
I live there alone,
and I don't have any cats,

29:14.586 --> 29:17.045
in case your allergic.

29:18.423 --> 29:20.299
I, um...

29:20.425 --> 29:22.718
I don't- I don't think
I should do that.

29:22.844 --> 29:24.720
No, you're probably right.

29:24.846 --> 29:26.138
It's late.

29:26.264 --> 29:29.516
I mean, you're probably
really tired anyway.

29:29.642 --> 29:31.143
Can I ask you something?

29:31.269 --> 29:35.022
How come you picked me up,
gave me a ride?

29:35.148 --> 29:36.732
I don't know.

29:36.858 --> 29:38.817
I don't-I don't know why.

29:38.943 --> 29:40.360
I don't know.

29:48.953 --> 29:50.204
Okay, I hope you don't mind.

29:50.330 --> 29:51.580
I just haven't-

29:51.706 --> 29:56.543
I just, you know, haven't kissed
a man in a long time.

29:56.669 --> 30:00.756
I just forgot how good it feels.

30:00.882 --> 30:02.508
Okay, thank you for the ride.

30:02.634 --> 30:04.343
Maybe I'll see you around.

30:04.469 --> 30:05.594
Okay.

30:23.947 --> 30:26.990
Yeah!
- Whoo!

30:34.499 --> 30:38.335
Hey, you're late again.

30:38.461 --> 30:39.503
Get down there and get dressed

30:39.629 --> 30:41.255
and get on
the fucking stage now.

30:53.101 --> 30:55.394
We need to talk now.

30:56.604 --> 30:58.730
Well, lookie, lookie, Cookie.

30:58.857 --> 30:59.982
No, don't stop.

31:00.108 --> 31:02.985
It just got
a lot more interesting.

31:03.111 --> 31:05.153
So come on
and join the party, sweetcakes.

31:05.280 --> 31:09.700
We are on lesson number three,
the day you were absent.

31:11.244 --> 31:13.203
Oh, no, you did not
touch the 'do.

31:13.329 --> 31:14.288
Oh, yeah.

31:14.414 --> 31:15.956
Fuck your 'do,
and fuck your whores.

31:16.082 --> 31:17.416
Who you calling a whore,
you little bitch?

31:17.542 --> 31:18.500
I don't see what else-

31:18.626 --> 31:22.129
No, no, no,
Cookie, Cookie, Cookie.

31:22.255 --> 31:23.338
Go upstairs.

31:23.464 --> 31:25.215
We'll finish up later.

31:30.346 --> 31:32.890
All right.

31:33.016 --> 31:35.893
So...

31:36.019 --> 31:38.604
What are we talking about here,
Johnny?

31:38.730 --> 31:39.771
I don't understand.
Tell me-

31:39.898 --> 31:40.856
We're talking about my son.

31:40.982 --> 31:42.149
We're talking about my son.

31:42.275 --> 31:43.859
I cannot work on Christmas Eve.

31:43.985 --> 31:45.110
I have to be with him.

31:45.236 --> 31:46.737
Your son needs you to work,

31:46.863 --> 31:48.280
and he needs you to work
very hard.

31:48.406 --> 31:50.657
Don't you fucking tell me
what's best for my kid.

31:50.783 --> 31:51.825
I swear to God.

31:51.951 --> 31:54.036
The kid would not
know the difference

31:54.162 --> 31:56.538
whether you're there or not.

31:56.664 --> 31:57.998
Goddamn it.

31:58.124 --> 32:02.336
Johnny, I have been easy on you,

32:02.462 --> 32:04.129
because when I watch you dance,

32:04.255 --> 32:08.800
I get a raging boner,
and so do a lot of other people.

32:08.927 --> 32:10.469
But on Christmas Eve,

32:10.595 --> 32:15.807
I'm gonna have a lot of very
lonely people out in my club,

32:15.934 --> 32:19.645
some even thinking
about killing themselves,

32:19.771 --> 32:22.439
and they come here
looking for companionship.

32:22.565 --> 32:25.317
