for a little bit of love.

32:25.443 --> 32:27.152
They are looking
for a little bit of hope.

32:27.278 --> 32:29.321
What about- what about
one of the girls who's Jewish?

32:29.447 --> 32:30.781
What about them?
Why can't they work?

32:30.907 --> 32:32.741
That is not the point.

32:32.867 --> 32:34.826
All the dancing that goes on
on that stage

32:34.953 --> 32:37.204
is nothing but an expensive
advertisement

32:37.330 --> 32:41.249
for the main attraction
in the fucking blue room.

32:41.376 --> 32:43.293
Well, I am not a whore.

32:44.504 --> 32:47.381
Well, then you better learn,
Johnny,

32:47.507 --> 32:50.842
'cause you are costing me
$1,000 a head

32:50.969 --> 32:53.762
every time you don't give any.

32:53.888 --> 32:55.847
Let me put it this way.

32:55.974 --> 32:59.017
If you are not here
on Christmas Eve,

32:59.143 --> 33:03.397
you should consider getting
a job at Wally's Whack Shack.

33:03.523 --> 33:05.357
We clear?

33:05.483 --> 33:06.525
Yeah.

33:38.599 --> 33:40.559
You all right?

33:40.685 --> 33:43.937
Everything all right?

33:44.063 --> 33:46.815
Just leave me alone.

33:46.941 --> 33:48.066
It's getting colder.

33:48.192 --> 33:51.028
You're gonna get sick
dressed like that.

33:51.154 --> 33:54.698
Why don't you just fuck off?

33:54.824 --> 33:56.241
Listen, I'm not gonna
go back in

33:56.367 --> 33:59.036
until I know you're all right.

33:59.162 --> 34:00.245
You don't have to rush.

34:00.371 --> 34:01.913
Just take your time.

34:08.045 --> 34:10.797
Do you have a smoke?

34:10.922 --> 34:13.050
Yeah, sure.

34:21.016 --> 34:22.141
You're not from around here,
are you?

34:22.268 --> 34:25.270
No, I'm just passing through.

34:29.317 --> 34:31.193
Yeah, I thought so.

34:31.319 --> 34:32.777
You're too nice.

34:37.533 --> 34:39.951
Thanks.

34:40.078 --> 34:42.329
Where are you from?

34:42.455 --> 34:43.746
San Francisco.

34:43.873 --> 34:45.415
Moved down here
about a year ago.

34:47.668 --> 34:49.628
What's your name?

34:49.754 --> 34:50.754
Scarlet.

34:51.714 --> 34:53.507
Scarlet.

34:53.632 --> 34:54.882
I'm Jack.

34:57.804 --> 34:59.137
Were you in here
the other night?

34:59.347 --> 35:01.056
No.

35:01.182 --> 35:04.559
You sure?

35:04.685 --> 35:06.436
'Cause I don't forget eyes
like yours.

35:07.522 --> 35:09.439
I'm sure.

35:09.565 --> 35:10.690
Get dressed.

35:10.817 --> 35:11.983
You got a request
for a private.

35:16.781 --> 35:18.824
Whoa.

35:18.950 --> 35:21.326
I got to go.

35:21.452 --> 35:23.245
Can I see you again?

35:23.371 --> 35:24.371
Yeah, yeah.

35:24.497 --> 35:26.373
Just request me, Scarlet.

35:26.499 --> 35:27.707
Wait for me in the blue room.

35:34.006 --> 35:35.006
Here.

35:35.133 --> 35:39.010
Oh.
- Thanks.

35:39.137 --> 35:40.846
Okay.

35:53.985 --> 35:55.861
Hey, papa.

35:55.987 --> 35:58.655
I hope I didn't keep you
too long.

35:58.781 --> 36:01.241
I'll make it up to you.

36:01.367 --> 36:04.327
First one's on me.

36:20.970 --> 36:22.262
This is your first time,
isn't it?

36:22.388 --> 36:24.514
Yeah, let's-

36:24.640 --> 36:26.391
why don't we just talk first?

36:26.517 --> 36:29.102
Most men don't pay me to talk.

36:29.228 --> 36:32.105
And the ones who do are trying
to talk me into something else.

36:32.231 --> 36:34.941
But I'm telling you,
I don't do anything but dance.

36:35.067 --> 36:36.526
I don't want anything.

36:36.652 --> 36:39.029
Let's just talk like
we were doing before.

36:49.916 --> 36:53.043
Come dance with me.

36:53.169 --> 36:54.336
Here?
No.

36:54.462 --> 36:56.796
No, I-I'm not good at that.

36:56.923 --> 36:58.215
Yes, it will be fun.

36:58.341 --> 37:00.091
I got old legs.

37:00.218 --> 37:04.137
They might be old,
but they're not dead.

37:04.263 --> 37:07.432
And it's a slow song.

38:00.486 --> 38:02.612
Just stop.

38:05.116 --> 38:07.450
Are you afraid of me?

38:07.576 --> 38:09.744
I'm old enough
to be your father.

38:09.870 --> 38:13.164
Most of them are.

38:20.464 --> 38:22.465
No, stop.

38:31.142 --> 38:36.187
Oh, sweet pea,
Mommy misses you so much.

38:39.150 --> 38:42.110
I just don't know
how much longer I can do this.

38:42.236 --> 38:45.071
I'm trying for you, baby.

38:46.824 --> 38:49.534
I miss you so much.

38:49.660 --> 38:52.620
I just feel like it's my fault.

39:15.895 --> 39:18.271
Arctic storms moving
into Northern California

39:18.397 --> 39:20.565
should cause temperatures
in the L.A. basin

39:20.691 --> 39:23.318
to drop as much as 25 degrees.

39:23.444 --> 39:25.445
Although temperatures have been
within normal ranges

39:25.571 --> 39:26.863
for this holiday season,

39:26.989 --> 39:28.907
these temps are highly unusual.

