Come on, Lucky.

40:29.802 --> 40:31.594
Excuse me, miss,
may I check your purse?

40:31.720 --> 40:32.679
No, you may not.

40:32.805 --> 40:34.139
I'm not asking
for your permission.

40:34.265 --> 40:35.557
Are you accusing me
of something?

40:35.683 --> 40:37.934
Say, sweetie, there you are.

40:38.060 --> 40:39.978
I was looking for you.

40:40.104 --> 40:41.521
Is everything okay?
- Store security.

40:41.647 --> 40:43.022
I need to check her purse.

40:43.149 --> 40:44.941
Oh, you know what?

40:45.067 --> 40:46.401
This is my fault.

40:46.527 --> 40:48.069
It's a collector's edition,

40:48.195 --> 40:49.904
and I told her
that I paid for it already,

40:50.030 --> 40:53.199
but I got sidetracked.

40:53.325 --> 40:56.453
Can-can we just let this slide?

40:59.999 --> 41:00.999
Hey.

41:01.125 --> 41:02.667
Hey, hey, hey.

41:02.793 --> 41:04.419
Get your hands off me!

41:04.545 --> 41:06.838
All right.

41:06.964 --> 41:09.007
Here.

41:11.469 --> 41:13.303
Must be for someone special,
huh?

41:20.144 --> 41:21.561
Why are you following me?

41:22.980 --> 41:27.358
I just-
let me buy you some lunch, okay?

41:27.485 --> 41:30.361
Your choice.

41:30.488 --> 41:31.571
I just want to talk.

41:43.042 --> 41:45.960
There you go.

41:46.086 --> 41:49.339
Well, you're just filled
with little tricks, aren't you?

41:49.465 --> 41:51.049
Here's your dessert.

41:51.175 --> 41:53.218
Thanks.
- Enjoy.

41:53.344 --> 41:55.136
So what brings you
to this city?

41:55.262 --> 42:00.016
Well, what brings anyone
to this city?

42:00.142 --> 42:02.060
I wanted to be a somebody.

42:02.186 --> 42:03.645
Is that so much to ask?

42:04.522 --> 42:05.939
You sound like a nonbeliever.

42:06.065 --> 42:07.732
No, this city just has a way

42:07.858 --> 42:10.485
of crushing your dreams
pretty fast.

42:12.154 --> 42:13.238
Well, what about your parents.

42:13.364 --> 42:15.448
Were they for it?

42:21.205 --> 42:24.249
My mother just recently
passed away,

42:24.375 --> 42:27.585
and my father died
in a boating accident

42:27.711 --> 42:30.797
before I was born.

42:30.923 --> 42:33.258
That's what she told me, anyway.

42:33.384 --> 42:35.301
You have doubts?

42:35.427 --> 42:39.806
I don't know.

42:39.932 --> 42:45.103
I used to catch her staring off
into somewhere for hours,

42:45.229 --> 42:49.107
like she knows
that he's still around.

42:53.571 --> 42:54.946
Can I tell you a secret?

42:55.072 --> 42:58.908
Yeah, sure.

42:59.034 --> 43:01.327
I see my father all the time.

43:02.663 --> 43:03.955
How?

43:04.081 --> 43:10.295
In my sleep,
especially when I was younger.

43:10.421 --> 43:12.338
See, he likes to travel
the world,

43:12.464 --> 43:14.841
and if I'm good,

43:14.967 --> 43:17.969
then sometimes
he'll take me with him

43:18.095 --> 43:20.638
and share his adventures
with me.

43:20.764 --> 43:21.931
And what's he like?

43:22.057 --> 43:26.352
He's handsome,
and he has strong hands

43:26.478 --> 43:28.229
and a very gentle heart.

43:28.355 --> 43:30.773
I mean, he couldn't hurt a fly
if he wanted to.

43:34.612 --> 43:37.363
And he has eyes like yours,

43:37.489 --> 43:41.618
all mysterious
and full of secrets.

43:45.289 --> 43:48.249
I'm sorry, I don't mean
to make you feel uncomfortable.

43:49.501 --> 43:51.502
It's okay.
Don't apologize.

43:51.629 --> 43:54.005
I just really like
talking to you.

43:54.131 --> 43:57.383
I really like talking
to you too.

44:03.390 --> 44:05.683
You know what time it is?

44:05.809 --> 44:06.893
I don't have a watch-

44:07.019 --> 44:08.895
I got to go.
I'm late for work.

44:09.021 --> 44:11.356
I can't afford
to lose another job.

44:11.482 --> 44:12.649
You'll come in and see me?

44:12.775 --> 44:14.359
Yeah.

44:14.485 --> 44:16.194
All right.

44:16.320 --> 44:18.446
Thanks.

44:18.572 --> 44:19.989
Don't stop believing.

44:21.450 --> 44:22.742
Only in miracles, Jack.

45:04.952 --> 45:05.952
Hi.
- Hey.

45:06.078 --> 45:07.829
I'm Nicole.

45:07.955 --> 45:09.205
Hey.

45:09.331 --> 45:11.040
I'm-my name's Qwerty.

45:11.166 --> 45:12.125
I know.

45:12.251 --> 45:14.502
It's on your name tag.

45:15.546 --> 45:17.880
Is this your first time?

45:18.006 --> 45:19.507
Yeah.

45:19.633 --> 45:20.883
Is it that obvious?

45:21.009 --> 45:22.218
It's also my first time.

45:22.344 --> 45:25.430
You know, at first,
I didn't really want to come.

45:25.556 --> 45:27.265
I didn't want
to seem desperate,

45:27.391 --> 45:29.642
like I need help
in meeting someone.

45:29.768 --> 45:35.189
But then I realized I haven't
been on a date in-in two years.

45:35.315 --> 45:38.067
So, here I am.

45:39.069 --> 45:40.945
Are-are you coming inside?

45:41.071 --> 45:45.825
Yeah, of course,
of course.

45:45.951 --> 45:46.951
Is everything all right?

45:47.077 --> 45:49.787
I'm sorry; I think
I'm losing circulation.

45:49.913 --> 45:51.164
Where?

45:51.290 --> 45:52.749
Just here in my right leg.

45:52.875 --> 45:54.208
Can I get you some water
or something?

45:54.334 --> 45:55.918
Are you-

46:00.758 --> 46:02.008
Help!

46:30.788 --> 46:32.789
Hi.

46:32.915 --> 46:36.459
Hey.

46:36.585 --> 46:39.545
I haven't seen you around
in a few days.

46:44.635 --> 46:46.928
I was such an idiot
the other night.

46:47.054 --> 46:49.347
I don't know
what came over me,

46:49.473 --> 46:52.809
but I apologize
if I was being too forward.

46:54.144 --> 46:56.813
It's been a very long time
for me too.

47:06.782 --> 47:08.157
You finished?
You're off?

47:08.283 --> 47:11.285
Yeah, it's been slow.

47:12.496 --> 47:15.873
If-if you want some company,
I could-

47:15.999 --> 47:19.460
If you-if you'd like,
I could take you home.

47:19.586 --> 47:20.628
I mean, if you want,
I could-

47:20.754 --> 47:22.088
Yeah, no, I-
yeah, I would like that.

47:22.214 --> 47:23.214
I would.

47:23.340 --> 47:25.883
Great.

47:29.638 --> 47:30.596
But not tonight.

47:30.722 --> 47:32.390
I can't.

47:32.516 --> 47:33.766
That's him.

47:33.892 --> 47:37.812
He called, you know, right-
shortly after I got home.

47:37.938 --> 47:41.566
