to give him something

01:22:15.805 --> 01:22:19.642
that I could never give him.

01:22:19.768 --> 01:22:20.768
So he left me.

01:22:38.119 --> 01:22:40.454
Who's gonna love me,
big daddy-o?

01:22:44.417 --> 01:22:46.293
