01:24:11.546 --> 01:24:15.007
Faster than
the speed of sound.

01:24:15.133 --> 01:24:16.842
Wonderful.

01:24:16.968 --> 01:24:20.429
I will take a one-way ticket
to Paris, please.

01:24:20.555 --> 01:24:22.139
All right.

01:24:22.265 --> 01:24:23.515
Here we go.
