01:31:26.981 --> 01:31:31.234
God bless you, sister.

01:31:31.360 --> 01:31:33.528
God bless you.

01:33:18.134 --> 01:33:22.387
I didn't call last night
because I-

01:33:22.513 --> 01:33:24.556
